        <div class="reveal">
          <h2 style="color:var(--primary); margin-bottom:1rem;">Our Mission &amp; Purpose</h2>
          <p>The purpose of this website is simple: to provide the most comprehensive, easy-to-use, and up-to-date informational guide for Mellow Mushroom fans. We noticed that finding consistent pricing estimates, detailed nutrition facts, and comprehensive dining guides all in one place was difficult. We exist to solve that problem.</p>
          <p style="margin-top:1rem;">We compile customer resources, menus, and dining tips into beautifully designed, accessible formats to help you plan your next meal, family gathering, or catering event.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal delay-100">
          <div class="tips-box" style="margin:0; border-left-color:var(--danger); background:#fff5f5;">
            <h3 style="color:var(--danger); margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Not Affiliated Statement</h3>
            <p><strong>IMPORTANT:</strong> This website is an independent informational website. We are <strong>NOT</strong> affiliated, associated, authorized, endorsed by, or in any way officially connected with Mellow Mushroom, its franchisees, or any of its subsidiaries or its affiliates.</p>
            <p style="margin-top:1rem;">All product names, logos, and brands are property of their respective owners. Prices shown are estimates and vary by location.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

