  <!-- Editorial Process & Timeline -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid-2-col" style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap:3rem;">
        
        <div class="reveal">
          <h2>Our Editorial Process</h2>
          <p>Content accuracy is our top priority. We know menu prices and items change. Because most Mellow Mushroom locations are franchised and set their own prices, providing exact national pricing is impossible. Instead, we use a rigorous process to provide the best possible estimates.</p>
          
          <div class="timeline">
            <div class="timeline-item">
              <h4>1. Data Collection</h4>
              <p>We aggregate menus, prices, and customer reports from various locations nationwide.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
              <h4>2. Menu Updates &amp; Verification</h4>
              <p>We cross-reference our data regularly to catch seasonal menu changes and price hikes.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
              <h4>3. Content Creation</h4>
              <p>We format this data into user-friendly, responsive tables and comprehensive guides.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
              <h4>4. Community Feedback</h4>
              <p>We rely on users to report incorrect prices or broken links, adjusting our estimates accordingly.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal delay-100">
          <h2>Why Visitors Trust Us</h2>
          <p>We don't hide behind corporate speak. We clearly state our independent nature and provide information transparently. Visitors trust this website because we put the user experience first—no annoying pop-ups, fast loading times, and straight-to-the-point information.</p>
          
